{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "b6f2a1a0-4e2a-4b7a-9c2d-miamngo-api-v13",
    "name": "API Miam N Go - Production v1.3",
    "description": "# API Miam N Go\n\nAPI REST Laravel 12 + Sanctum pour la plateforme de commande et livraison de repas Miam N Go.\n\n**Base URL (production)** : `https://api-miamngo.digiapp.tech/api`\n\n**Sécurité** : Laravel Sanctum avec Bearer Token. Les routes protégées nécessitent le header `Authorization: Bearer {{token}}`.\n\n**Rôles** :\n- `ADMIN` : accès total à toutes les ressources.\n- `PARTNER` : gère uniquement les produits/commandes/paiements/livraisons liés à son ou ses restaurant(s) (table `partner_users`).\n- `CUSTOMER` : gère uniquement son propre profil, ses commandes, ses paiements et ses livraisons.\n\n**Référentiel des statuts métier (v1.3)** :\n- `status_order` : PENDING, CONFIRMED, PREPARING, READY, COMPLETED, CANCELLED, REJECTED\n- `status_payment` : PENDING, PROCESSING, PAID, FAILED, REFUNDED, CANCELLED\n- `status_delivery` : PENDING, ASSIGNED, PICKED_UP, ON_THE_WAY, DELIVERED, FAILED, CANCELLED\n\nCycle recommandé commande : `PENDING -> CONFIRMED -> PREPARING -> READY -> COMPLETED`\nCycle recommandé livraison : `PENDING -> ASSIGNED -> PICKED_UP -> ON_THE_WAY -> DELIVERED`\n\n**Repository** : https://github.com/BabyBossKfy/miam_n_go\n**Framework** : Laravel 12 + Sanctum\n**Auteur documentation** : Franck Kianguebeni\n**Version documentation source** : v1.3 consolidée (16 juillet 2026)\n\nCollection générée à partir de `API_Miam_N_Go_Production_Auth_Roles_v1_3_Consolide.pdf`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "test",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Capture automatiquement le token retourne par /auth/login ou /auth/register",
          "if (pm.response.code === 200 || pm.response.code === 201) {",
          "    try {",
          "        const body = pm.response.json();",
          "        const token = body.token || (body.data && body.data.token);",
          "        if (token) {",
          "            pm.collectionVariables.set('token', token);",
          "        }",
          "    } catch (e) { /* reponse non JSON, on ignore */ }",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "https://api-miamngo.digiapp.tech/api", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string", "description": "Token Bearer courant (auto-rempli après login/register)" },
    { "key": "token_admin", "value": "", "type": "string", "description": "Token Bearer d'un compte ADMIN" },
    { "key": "token_partner", "value": "", "type": "string", "description": "Token Bearer d'un compte PARTNER" },
    { "key": "token_customer", "value": "", "type": "string", "description": "Token Bearer d'un compte CUSTOMER" },
    { "key": "category_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "partner_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "product_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "customer_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "order_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "payment_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "delivery_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "01. Authentification",
      "description": "Inscription, connexion, profil utilisateur connecté et déconnexion. Ces routes gèrent la génération et l'usage du token Sanctum.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Inscription client (register)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"first_name_customers\": \"Franck\",\n  \"last_name_customers\": \"Kianguebeni\",\n  \"phone_customers\": \"066000001\",\n  \"mail_customers\": \"franck2@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"password_confirmation\": \"password123\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Route publique. Crée un compte CUSTOMER et retourne un token Sanctum utilisable immédiatement."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Connexion (login)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"mail_customers\": \"partner@godfavor.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Route publique. Retourne le token, le type Bearer, l'utilisateur et son rôle (ADMIN, PARTNER ou CUSTOMER). Le script de test de cette requête enregistre automatiquement le token dans la variable de collection `token`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Utilisateur connecté (me)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/me",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "me"]
            },
            "description": "Route protégée (tous rôles). Retourne les informations de l'utilisateur authentifié par le token Bearer courant."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Déconnexion (logout)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/logout",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "logout"]
            },
            "description": "Route protégée (tous rôles). Révoque le token Sanctum courant."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
